\begin_inset Formula $C_{A_{1}A_{2}}=\left[A_{1H}^{\left(0\right)}\left(t\right),\hat{A}_{2H}^{\left(0\right)}\left(t^{'}\right)\right]$
\end_inset

 is also time-translationaly invariant because
\begin_inset Note Note
