\end_inset

) and will result in a more general form than 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\rho}_{n}=\frac{1}{w\left(\tilde{q}\right)}\hat{\Omega}\left(\tilde{q}\right)\hat{\rho}\hat{\Omega}^{\dagger}\left(\tilde{q}\right)$
\end_inset

 (see Eq.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:final indirect measurement"

\end_inset

).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(Section 2.8 of 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "BraginskyQM"

\end_inset

); also looked at section 2.2.6 of 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
