\end_inset

 which is more clearly written and organized with the rest of the measurement
 topics but not as physical; the connection between both sections is that
 the 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{W}$
\end_inset

/
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\Pi}$
\end_inset

 are the 
\emph on
