key "nielsenQI"

\end_inset

 - this is a convenient formalism to use if one only cares about measurement
 statistics and not the state the initial density operator collapses to.
 Moreover, the operators 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\Omega}\left(\tilde{q}\right)$
\end_inset

